# Legal Clause Classification using BERT

## Project Overview
This project focuses on fine-tuning the **BERT-base-uncased** model to classify legal document clauses. It was developed as a software simulation for the Computer Engineering Department at **Al-Farabi University College**.

## Features
* **Model:** BERT-base-uncased.
* **Analysis:** Ablation study comparing 256 vs 512 tokens.
* **Visualization:** Performance charts showing Macro F1-Score.
* **Success Metric:** Achieved **0.78**, exceeding the required 0.75 threshold.

